Package: nginx-torblocker
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         nginx (>= 1.18.0)
Description: Nginx module to block Tor exit nodes
 This module provides functionality to automatically block
 requests from Tor exit nodes. It reads a list of exit node
 IPs from a file and blocks requests from those addresses.
 Features include per-location configuration and automatic
 list reloading.
